<li>BB awarding, MReader deadline, follow-up, consultation</li>
</ol></div><div style="margin:20px 3px 3px 3px;padding-top:6px;padding-bottom:3px;padding-left:7px;background-color:lightsteelblue">成績評価の方法</div><div style="margin:10px"><p>15% Exam 1</p>
